      </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="col-md-8">
      <div class="panel panel-primary">
        <div class="panel-heading"><p style="font-size: 28px; margin-bottom: 2px;">Welcome to Trackplan Software Help Guide</p>
            <p><i>Powerful facilities Management Software and CAFM solution</i></p>
        </div>
        <div class="panel-body">
            <p>  On the left hand side of the screen you will see various different sections. These sections pertain to different areas of the software. On clicking these sections various sub-sections will appear to help narrow down the search of documentation needed. At the top of these sub-sections videos will also be provided. These videos were created with the vision of quickly helping our customers get up and running with the software.</p> Also on the top menu you will find the following: 
              <ul>

                <li style="padding:10px 0 10px 0;"><b>Help Guide</b> -this returns you to the homepage of the help guide.</li>

                <li style="padding-bottom:10px;"><b>Videos</b> - here you can find all of our video tutorials on our Youtube channel, this is updated regularly to keep you up to date with the latest features.</li>
                <li style="padding-bottom:10px;"><b>Updates</b> - here you can find all the latest product releases and newest features that have been added.</li>

                <li style="padding-bottom:10px;"><b>FAQ</b> - here you can find the most commonly asked questions in relation to the product.</li>
                <li style="padding-bottom:10px;"><b>Feedback</b> - This is used to send us feeback on the product and also ask us any questions in relation to the product. Feedback is greatly appreciated.</li>
                <li style="padding-bottom:10px;"><b>Contractor Portal</b> - this area applies specifically to the contractor portal section of the software. Any contractor using the software should visit here.</li>

                <li style="padding-bottom:10px;"><b>Search</b> - the search box is used to search all help articles on the site and return the ones most relevant to your search.</li>

              </ul>
              <h5>If you have any further questions, please contact us <b><a href="https://help.trackplanfm.com/submit-feedback/">here</a></b>.</h5>

        </div>
      </div>
